{"tid":2122802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"古思堯涉侮辱國旗 罹患末期直腸癌 官准保釋醫病","createTime":"2020-07-24T08:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T08:33:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfbe1abf11f970f4a1eb31a3fd084d7eb33c9d7","tid":2122802,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:03:04.000Z","msg":"患上直腸癌的社運人士古思堯，日前在西九龍法院舉起倒轉的五星紅旗，旗上寫有「黑色恐怖」、「白色恐怖」和「法西斯恐怖」等字句，遭拘控以侮辱國旗罪。古被捕後稱旗上的字由他寫上，為發洩不滿才犯案，早前在庭上更直言「我故意侮辱國旗」，還柙候訊。古思堯今日在西九龍裁判法院申請保釋，以便入院治療癌症，主任裁判官羅德泉批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/3W7TGIIFVRBP3DCBM4LOQ6WMIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2F3W7TGIIFVRBP3DCBM4LOQ6WMIE%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6P3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c18f5fef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2F3W7TGIIFVRBP3DCBM4LOQ6WMIE%2F&h=79ac1b09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/3W7TGIIFVRBP3DCBM4LOQ6WMIE/</a>"},{"pid":"f58ca8df8960fde85e7263c6480baa8e7edcf03a","tid":2122802,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e3c947c727916777eaf15fac73c186247c4af8","tid":2122802,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知仲有無幾年命仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554c621627454402540f130b2374d506dbbc0d93","tid":2122802,"uid":30084,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T08:06:33.000Z"